{"tid":2377983,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許樹昌：果欄確診個案增加　應考慮擴大受限區範圍","createTime":"2021-01-24T05:44:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T06:11:53.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"537b60bb058daf00aaa6c5c06dd63204fc291067","tid":2377983,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T05:44:50.000Z","msg":"政府抗疫督導委員會專家顧問許樹昌表示，今次佐敦封區，事前走漏風聲，可能令病毒隨著離開的人散出區外。他又認為，果欄一帶確診個案增加，當局應考慮擴大「受限區域」的範圍。<br />\n<br />\n另外，許樹昌認為，如果科興疫苗到下月中，仍未能提供詳細數據，當局應再研究是否需要調整策略，另選其他滅活疫苗。"},{"pid":"fe18e785163261f9ff058380e5cdcf7cd54349eb","tid":2377983,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T05:44:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572080-20210124.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572080-20210124.htm&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TamzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=3a183f9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572080-20210124.htm&h=766ef944\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572080-20210124.htm</a>"},{"pid":"bea6325cf947c3794c271f6c4e9d2449888861f3","tid":2377983,"uid":237459,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T05:45:42.000Z","msg":"香港已經輸咗"},{"pid":"d9bbd0e3ddf1393a6206743ce84926142be5dc7f","tid":2377983,"uid":304916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T05:46:10.000Z","msg":"不如成個油尖旺封哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e26f2062f6cdbd4c240eaf57efd55f832610458d","tid":2377983,"uid":357030,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T05:46:31.000Z","msg":"呢個所謂專家真係好黑人憎<br />\n日日出嚟9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93